Sample program of MapReduce GridDB connector

There is a program to run WordCount as sample program of the GridDB connector.

GSWordCount: WordCount program using a GridDB connector for MapReduce

This program executes a MapReduce job with the data in GridDB as the input source and then store the results in GridDB.
